US DOT (Department of Transportation)

1. World Area Code lookup table:
http://www.transtats.bts.gov/Download_Lookup.asp?Lookup=L_WORLD_AREA_CODES

2. World Area Code table:
2.1. Go to http://www.transtats.bts.gov/DL_SelectFields.asp?Table_ID=315&DB_Short_Name=Aviation%20Support%20Tables
2.2. Select all the fields
2.3. Download the file. The file name should be something like 495998804_T_WAC_COUNTRY_STATE.zip
2.4. Extract the compressed file

3. Area codes for every airport:
http://www.dot.gov/sites/dot.dev/files/docs/airports_codes.txt

